{"tid":476587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乍得政府發表聲明否認接受何志平賄款批出石油開採權","createTime":"2017-11-22T06:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T15:33:40.000Z","uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c206493ed25bffd3f43eded1e725834ab6c2add7","tid":476587,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"前民政事務局局長何志平涉嫌賄賂非洲官員, 在美國被拘控. 被指涉及事件的乍得政府發表聲明, 否認總統代比, 曾經接受二百萬美元賄款, 批出石油開採權, 批評美國的指控是可恥的虛構, 破壞乍得和代比的形象.<br />\n<br />\n        美國當局指何志平涉嫌代表一間中國能源公司, 透過塞內加爾前外長加迪奧, 與代比接觸, 並提供賄款, 換取石油開採權. 何志平與加迪奧周末在美國紐約被捕, 兩人被控觸犯反海外腐敗法和洗黑錢罪.<br />\n<br />\n        68歲的何志平初步出庭應訊後, 繼續還柙. 一旦罪名成立, 最高可判監20年.<br />\n<br />\n        香港中華能源基金會發聲明, 高度關注事件, 表示沒有授權基金會的副主席兼秘書長何志平, 從事商業行為.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20171122141326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20171122141326&d=%2BLDQ0cNhDhlIe2Hwpj%2B39BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=4fbe00b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20171122141326</a>"},{"pid":"cf1882eb38f18721fb1c43f961d13090ee69d438","tid":476587,"uid":90704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:03:09.000Z","msg":"成日話美國佬為石油乜乜乜<br />\n留名等睇要改口話全世界都為石油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ebecdc6076d9900a662e593da8e216a05e0960","tid":476587,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:21:07.000Z","msg":"ok 炸得"},{"pid":"ca9ee066f693aebd6ad2d4ef43157fe032e1f93e","tid":476587,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.b